829
00:51:05,280 --> 00:51:08,400
[SPEAKER_02] Da, vi pomažete ljudima u prodaji aplikacijskih tvrtki, zar ne?

830
00:51:08,480 --> 00:51:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] To je kratko.

831
00:51:08,880 --> 00:51:15,360
